g.text: Sheriff's OfficeOfficial ReportDate: __________Location: __________The undersigned Sheriff of this jurisdi-tion hereby declares the following:In light of recent disturbances and suspi-cious activity, an investigation is under-way to ensure the safety of all citizens. Law enforcement remains vigilant in un-covering unlawful operations and bring-ing those responsible to justice.All persons with information are urged to come forward. Confidentiality is assured.By Order of the Sheriff [Signature]
